dct_title_s: Stokes and High Point, New Jersey 1962 brochure front
dct_description_sm: Maps of Stokes State Forest in Sussex County, N.J. part of multi-page brochure. These sheets are the front and back covers of brochure featuring six photographs of park and tables and descriptions about of the lakes and waterways, camp grounds, picnic areas and hiking trails.
